<head>
    <title></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.staticfile.org/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.org/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.org/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/home.css?v=1.2" media="print">
</head>

<body>
#parse("static/vm/navbar.vm")

<div class="container">
    <div class="list-group">
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-danger">
            <h4 class="list-group-item-heading">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-warning-sign"></span> Unload Agent
            </h4>
            <p class="list-group-item-text">
                This will completely unload the java-tracer agent from the current JVM.
                After unloading, the web interface will become unreachable and all tracing will stop.
            </p>
        </a>
        <div class="list-group-item">
            <h5>What happens when you unload:</h5>
            <ul>
                <li>The interceptor is disabled — all woven <code>s()/e()</code> calls become no-ops</li>
                <li>The class transformer is removed from the JVM</li>
                <li>The Jetty web server is stopped</li>
                <li>All configuration and trace data is cleared</li>
                <li>The target application continues running normally</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="list-group-item" style="text-align: center;">
            <button class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" id="unload_btn" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#confirmModal">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-off"></span> Unload Agent Now
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="confirmModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header modal-header-danger">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                <h4 class="modal-title">Confirm Unload</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p><strong>Are you sure you want to unload the agent?</strong></p>
                <p>This action cannot be undone. The web interface will stop immediately after unloading.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" id="unload_confirm">Unload</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
jQuery('#unload_confirm').click(function() {
    jQuery.ajax({
        url: '/unload/exec',
        type: 'POST',
        success: function(data) {
            jQuery('#confirmModal').modal('hide');
            jQuery('#unload_btn').prop('disabled', true);
            jQuery('#unload_btn').html('<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span> Agent Unloaded');
            jQuery('#unload_btn').removeClass('btn-danger').addClass('btn-success');
            alert('Agent has been unloaded successfully. This page will become unreachable shortly.');
        },
        error: function(xhr) {
            alert('Unload request sent. If the server stops, the agent was unloaded successfully.');
        }
    });
});
</script>
</body>